data.text:
There are 22 new home communities in Strathcona County, a mix of high-rise and low-rise that are planned, under construction or recently completed. There are 1 condo communities in Strathcona County, with 26 floorplans and units for sale. There are 9 townhouse communities in Strathcona County, with 65 floorplans and units and 17 single-family home communities, with 159 floorplans and units for sale. The median price per square foot for a low-rise home is $294. There are 28 quick move-in homes in Strathcona County for sale. The most active developer in Strathcona County is Daytona Homes.
